      "content": "It's great that your skin is looking much better, but you should **not** stop taking your antibiotics without consulting your doctor. Finishing the entire course, even if you feel better, is crucial to completely kill off the infection and prevent it from coming back stronger. Stopping early can lead to antibiotic resistance, making future infections much harder to treat. Please finish all the medication as prescribed!",
